10
00:00:06,120 --> 00:00:06,560
Salgo por

11
00:00:06,560 --> 00:00:07,360
La Zaidía.

12
00:00:07,360 --> 00:00:07,640
Sol.

13
00:00:07,640 --> 00:00:08,640
Tranquilidad.

14
00:00:08,640 --> 00:00:09,400
Y de repente...

15
00:00:09,400 --> 00:00:10,560
